content=["<dl>",
"<dt><a href='#Section0'>Low-tension glaucoma</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section0'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Usually asymptomatic; this is a subset of open-angle glaucoma in which intra-ocular pressure is normal.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Intra-ocular pressure is normal.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section1'>Closed-angle glaucoma</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section1'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Presents acutely with pain and redness; a poorly reactive, mid-dilated pupil; nausea and vomiting; a hazy cornea; and blurred vision.May have intermittent pain on entering a dark room. [1]",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Gonioscopy reveals a closed angle.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section2'>High myopia</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section2'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Although the cup-to-disc ratio may be large, no cup-to-disc enlargement is documented.Intra-ocular pressure is normal.Visual field defects do not change over time. [1]",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Testing shows highly myopic refraction.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section3'>Ocular hypertension</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section3'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Characterised by increased intra-ocular pressure in the absence of evidence of damage to the nerve fibre layer. [1]",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Characterised by a normal visual field test and no enlargement of the cup-to-disc ratio over time.</p>",
"</dd>",
"</dl>"].join("\n");